1.Given two integers a and b in the form of strings. Return the last digit of ab.
Platform: GeeksforGeeks 
SOURCECODE : class Solution {
    public int getLastDigit(String a, String b) {

        if (b.equals("0"))
            return 1;

        int base = (a.charAt(a.length() - 1) - '0') % 10;

        int exp = 0;
        for (char c : b.toCharArray()) {
            exp = (exp * 10 + (c - '0')) % 4;
        }

        if (exp == 0) exp = 4;

        int ans = 1;
        for (int i = 0; i < exp; i++) {
            ans = (ans * base) % 10;
        }

        return ans;
    }
}
Link : https://www.geeksforgeeks.org/problems/find-last-digit-of-ab-for-large-numbers1936/1
